OL,3,CFarm fined for multiple health and
OL,4,Csafety breaches after bull escape
OL,6,FA farming business in Kent has been
OL,7,Ffined for multiple health and safety
OL,8,Fbreaches.
OL,10,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,11,Fsays Seymour Stevens Limited, which
OL,12,Foperates a beef and arable farm in
OL,13,FFaversham, placed employees and others
OL,14,Fat risk over many years, in an attempt
OL,15,Fto cut costs.
OL,17,FA site visit carried out in November
OL,18,F2022 identified multiple failings.
