OL,3,CFarm fined for multiple health and
OL,4,Csafety breaches after bull escape
OL,6,FBull pens were broken and rusty and
OL,7,Fconcerns were raised about their
OL,8,Fsuitability to contain a bull. The
OL,9,Ffollowing month a bull managed to
OL,10,Fescape the farm and was brought back
OL,11,Fby the Police.
OL,13,FOne of the barns, used as a through
OL,14,Froute by an employee, was deemed
OL,15,Funsafe to enter due to its poor
OL,16,Fstructural state. A number of
OL,17,Felectrical faults were also identified.
