OL,6,FIn another shed, the roof was
OL,7,Finsecurely fixed and was being weighed
OL,8,Fdown with a hay bale. Roof sheeting
OL,9,Fwas also in a state of disrepair and
OL,10,Fin some cases falling from buildings.
OL,12,FHSE inspector Peter Bruce said, "While
OL,13,Fagriculture accounts for just one
OL,14,Fpercent of the working population, it
OL,15,Faccounts for about 20 per cent of
OL,16,Fworkplace fatalities."
