OL,6,FThe company had previously been
OL,7,Finvited to attend paid-for "Preparing
OL,8,Ffor Inspection" courses but they
OL,9,Fdidn't take up the offer.
OL,11,FMr Bruce said, "Employees and members
OL,12,Fof the public were being put at risk,
OL,13,Fdespite previous warnings having been
OL,14,Fgiven to the company by their staff."
OL,16,F"It is important that employers
OL,17,Fmaintain their workplaces and
OL,18,Fequipment to suitable standards to
OL,19,Fensure that employees, visitors and
OL,20,Fmembers of the public are not put at
OL,21,Frisk."
